data.description: Castle'', Your opportunity to be ''King of the Hill''. The property offers million-dollar views, seclusion, serenity, and adjoins open spaces. The property borders the Dubois Municipal Airport. The 7,000 ft runway can accommodate your corporate jet. Located 45 minutes from Teton National Park. Property has a newly constructed home on approximately 20 acres The l20 acre lot could be subdivided as per Fremont county rules. The home has upscale architectural features throughout with a bonus room above the attached garage with it own exterior entrance. Underground utilities to the lots and home including water, power and fiber optic cable.  OWNER FINANICING POSSIBLE.  Terms negotiable contact listing agent.
